      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOMAX KEEPING (2) goes very well this trip starting five times for two wins and two minors. Hit the frame latest (30.06) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Rates on top and should go close. FASCINATE SAMUEL (8) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by half a length (29.27) at Gosford. Capable of going close again. GREAT CHAT (7) failed to come into contention last start at this track, but prior to that won easily by 3.5 lengths at Richmond (29.59) beating LAYLA'S LILLY in a Grade 5 on February 11. Has the ability to give this a shake. ELLE'S MOON (6) was below best last time at this track (30.44) in a Grade 5, finishing a 9 length seventh. Has already won out of this draw.",
